sources.description:
Wild Bill Hickok mistakes a young drifter for Billy the Kid. The consequences prove deadly, during an 1876 gold rush.
 
Original title: Deadwood '76 (1965)

Director: James Landis
Writers: Arch Hall Sr., James Landis 
Stars: Arch Hall Jr., Jack Lester, La Donna Cottier & Arch Hall Sr.
Genres: B movie, Color, Western
